I run into the same error with python3

    http.server.BaseHTTPRequestHandler.**init**(self, *args)

    self.handle()

    self.handle_one_request()
  File "/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.4/lib/python3.4/http/server.py", line 386, in handle_one_request
    method()
  File "/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.4/lib/python3.4/site-packages/tensorflow/tensorboard/tensorboard_handler.py", line 415, in do_GET
    handlers[clean_path](query_params)

    self._send_gzip_response(graph_pbtxt, 'text/plain')
